data.description: Only 2 years old with amazing views all around.  Situated on almost 20 acres, with about 5 acres fully fenced, this home is a Must See! Home boasts 1320 square feet with an additional 396 square foot family room addition.  Laminate plank flooring throughout. Kitchen has granite counter tops with white shaker cabinets and under-cabinet LED lighting. All appliances are brand new and include the refrigerator, 5 burner propane gas range, and dishwasher. Bathrooms have upgraded fixtures with Kohler toilets and custom tile. The Instant Hot Water heater is also propane gas.  Property also features Mohave Electric Power, well water, and over sized septic tank which will allow you to expand with a casita or garage with plumbing. The home has upgraded foam attic insulation, energy efficient central A.C with Heat Pump. Reflective roof tiles and low-e windows and all lighting fixtures are low maintenance. Siding is fiber-cement which is strong and low maintenance.   The detached garage has two roll up doors, the front door is 10 x 8 and the back door is 6 x 7 making it simple to head right out into the desert with your toys!  The garage also has two workshops on either side of it, both 10 x 21 in size with their own entrance and windows.  Plumbing and electrical is ready for install in the garage if you wish.  There's a nice area cleared out already for another building - casita, garage or whatever your heart desires.  Contact your Realtor today to see this little piece of desert paradise!
